    "specifications": "RNase Destroyer Sprayer: RNase Destroyer is ready to use and has more safty than traditional chemicals such as DEPC, a known carcinogen. RNase Destroyer, can be used to remove RNase and DNA contamination from bench, instruments, experiment tools, glass and plastic consumables. Ready to use right out of the bottle, these solutions leave no residue on work surfaces when used as directed. It is good for lab-ware and surfaces that can&rsquo;t be autoclaved.\nStorage Condition:\nStored in original containers.\nStored in a well-ventilated area.\nKeep containers securely sealed.\nProtect from light.\nProtect eyes.\nDo not mix with acids.\nStored at 2 to 30℃\nShelf Life: Valid for 6 months after sealing off.",
